Class SyndicationExtensionLoadedEventArgs

Provides data for the Loaded event.

Syntax
[Serializable]
public class SyndicationExtensionLoadedEventArgs : EventArgs, IComparable
Remarks

A Loaded event occurs whenever the Load(XmlReader) or Load(IXPathNavigable) methods are called.
